quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,27,"phir qayamat ke roz Allah unhen zaleel o khawar kere ga aur unn se kahe ga"" batao ab kahan hain mere woh shareek jin ke liye tum ( ahal haq se ) jhagrre kya karte thay ?"" jin logon ko duniya mein ilm haasil tha woh kahin ge"" aaj ruswai aur badbakhti hai kafiroon ke liye """
16,28,"haan, inhi kafiroon ke liye jo apne nafs par zulm karte hue jab mulaika ke hathon girftar hotay hain to ( sar kashi chore kar ) foran dagain (hatyar)daal dete hain aur kehte hain"" hum to koi qasoor nahi kar rahay thay"" mulaika jawab dete hain"" kar kaisay nahi rahay thay! Allah tumahray krtoton se khoob waaqif hai"
16,29,"ab jao, jahannum ke darwazon mein ghis jao wahein tum ko hamesha rehna hai"" pas haqeeqat yeh hai ke bara hi bura thikana hai mtkbron ke liye"
16,30,"doosri taraf jab khuda taras logon se poocha jata hai ke yeh kya cheez hai jo tumahray rab ki taraf se nazil hui hai, to woh jawab dete hain ke"" behtareen cheez utri hai"" iss terhan ke nekokaar logon ke liye iss duniya mein bhi bhalai hai aur akhirat ka ghar to zaroor hi un ke haq mein behtar hai bara acha ghar hai Muttaqiyun ka"
16,31,"daimi qiyam ki jannaten, jin mein woh daakhil hon ge, neechay nhrin beh rahi hongi, aur sab kuch wahan ain unn ki khwahish ke mutabiq hoga yeh jaza deta hai Allah Muttaqiyun ko"
16,32,"unn Muttaqiyun ko jin ki roohein pakizgee ki haalat mein jab mulaika qabz karte hain to kehte hain"" salam ho tum par, jao jannat mein apne aamaal ke badlay """
16,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ab jo yeh log intzaar kar rahay hain to iss ke siwa ab aur kya baqi reh gaya hai ke mulaika hi aa pohnchain, ya tairay rab ka faisla sadir ho jaye? iss terhan ki dhatai inn se pehlay bohat se log kar chuke hain phir jo kuch unn ke sath howa woh unn par Allah ka zulm nah tha balkay unn ka apna zulm tha jo onhon ne khud apne oopar kya"
16,34,unn ke krtoton ki kharabian aakhir unn ki damangeer ho gayeen aur wohi cheez unn par musallat ho kar rahi jis ka woh mazaq uraya karte thay
